item.title: Krabby Patty Crisis
item.description: A loud fight, or rather, a loud tournament in fights without rules between cartoon characters is waiting for you in this game. Stretch your fingers, clean your mouse, check your keyboard and join the fight! First, choose who you will manage. Several characters from the most popular cartoons are available. Unfortunately, the game does not provide a mode for two.
